Class TimeQuantity

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.volcanoes.core.quakeml.TimeQuantity

  • public class TimeQuantity
extends Object
    This class represents a point in time, with optional symmetric or asymmetric uncertainties given in seconds. Modeled after QuakeML TimeQuanity element.
    Author:
    Diana Norgaard
